description: Semantic extension of the Malay Jakun, an indigenous ethnic group inhabiting the jungles of Pahang, Johor and Negeri Sembilan.

adjectives.description: jakun (comparative more jakun, superlative most jakun)

entries.meaning: (informal, derogatory, Singapore) Fascinated by objects, events, or experiences which seem ordinary to others.
(informal, offensive, Malaysia) Overly excited, bad-tempered, unruly, or unsophisticated.
